1
00:00:57,982 --> 00:01:00,958
=Within The Grip=

2
00:01:00,958 --> 00:01:02,928
=Episode 17=

3
00:01:02,928 --> 00:01:06,950
(Have No One to Trust)

4
00:01:10,719 --> 00:01:13,390
The Yunya Temple hosted
a vegetarian banquet for the donors.

5
00:01:13,792 --> 00:01:15,760
I saw Gu Zhaoxi before the banquet.

6
00:01:16,280 --> 00:01:19,799
I chased after him
to the back courtyard but lost my way.

7
00:01:20,319 --> 00:01:21,560
When I found my way back,

8
00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:25,359
I found those people gathered
around the corpse and that pouch.

9
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:28,519
These represent
our family's sincere gesture.

10
00:01:28,879 --> 00:01:31,120
If you need anything,
please don't hesitate to ask.

11
00:01:31,519 --> 00:01:33,400
Our family will provide full assistance.

12
00:01:34,319 --> 00:01:37,159
Master Chaosheng, the banquet
is about to begin. We should head over.

13
00:01:40,760 --> 00:01:43,120
(Yunya Temple)
(Zhaoxi? Why would he be here?)

14
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:46,480
Why is there a corpse?

15
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:47,560
Stop looking! Step back.

16
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:49,079
Yes, and right inside the temple.

17
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:55,560
Why is there a corpse here?

18
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:56,560
Everyone, look!

19
00:01:57,439 --> 00:01:58,879
- Someone's dead!
- Someone's dead!

20
00:02:01,239 --> 00:02:02,680
Stop looking. Step back.

21
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:14,759
So you were supposed to be

22
00:02:15,439 --> 00:02:19,360
at the temple banquet, but you ran into
someone who looked like Zhaoxi.

23
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:21,159
That was Gu Zhaoxi.

24
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:25,759
Zhaoxi was by my side the entire day.

25
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:30,479
If you didn't mistake him, perhaps
someone deliberately set this up.

26
00:03:05,760 --> 00:03:08,320
(Prince Consort seeks
painters to paint plum blossoms.)

27
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:14,039
Weren't you the person who set this up?

28
00:03:15,199 --> 00:03:16,639
What do you mean by that?

29
00:03:17,599 --> 00:03:21,759
Wasn't it you two conspiring
to lure me into this trap to control me?

30
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:26,319
If we wanted to control you,
why would we bother with all this?

31
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:27,060
You...

32
00:03:27,479 --> 00:03:29,560
You thought the assassin
you hired succeeded

33
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:32,319
until you later discovered
that Leng Yan failed.

34
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:35,400
That's why you wanted
to kill Wanniang to silence her.

35
00:03:35,719 --> 00:03:37,080
I still want to help you even now.

36
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:40,759
Why don't you tell me how you came up
with the idea to hire Leng Yan?

37
00:03:41,719 --> 00:03:44,520
Who told you Zhaoxi wasn't your brother?

38
00:03:45,039 --> 00:03:47,240
And who introduced Physician Li to you?

39
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:50,360
I truly didn't care about your life.

40
00:03:50,599 --> 00:03:53,199
But the one hiding behind
keeps stirring things up.

41
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:57,960
If you turn against each other,
he would likely be the real winner.

42
00:03:58,719 --> 00:04:01,240
(Top scholar, General Shen,)

43
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:04,680
(Crown Prince Yin Zhou, the Gu family,)

44
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:09,039
(Xuanji Pavilion...
They're all involved.)

45
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:19,319
For so many years, you've managed
our shops meticulously.

46
00:04:19,759 --> 00:04:22,240
Your desire to become
the family head is understandable.

47
00:04:22,879 --> 00:04:24,120
But the family is one body.

48
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:28,040
What you've done is no different
from severing your own limbs.

49
00:04:28,639 --> 00:04:32,920
Even if you became the family head,
could you truly secure that position?

50
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:35,519
But I am a bit curious.

51
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:38,639
Why did you come to believe
Zhaoxi isn't your brother?

52
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,199
No one put me up to it.

53
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:45,920
I overheard it

54
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:49,759
the day I went to report
the shops' revenue to Father.

55
00:04:51,160 --> 00:04:53,160
Master, the task failed.

56
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:59,560
Physician Qin knows the Mobei terrain
extremely well and escaped.

57
00:05:00,439 --> 00:05:03,920
But he said he would take the matter
of Master Zhaoxi to his grave,

58
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:05,600
not only to save our family's face,

59
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:07,920
but also to protect
his brother's last bloodline.

60
00:05:10,439 --> 00:05:13,920
Was that why Xuanwu sought
to pledge his allegiance to you?

61
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:17,519
Of course not. They didn't find me.

62
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:22,639
I heard Father intended to betroth you
to Zhaoxi as Xuanji Pavilion Master.

63
00:05:24,519 --> 00:05:26,144
That's when I understood

64
00:05:27,904 --> 00:05:30,079
he was going to hand over
the family to an outsider.

65
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:33,680
So I went to Gu Xuanwu.

66
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:36,920
He didn't know I overheard
their talk that day.

67
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:39,399
Xuanji is away studying poisons.

68
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:41,040
Wenshuang is into martial arts.

69
00:05:41,879 --> 00:05:43,439
Neither cares about the family affairs.

70
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:46,800
He knows what's good for himself.

71
00:05:47,519 --> 00:05:50,560
He knew only I could help him
reclaim the Xuanji Pavilion,

72
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:53,800
so he chose to submit to me.

73
00:05:54,879 --> 00:05:56,439
"Submit to you?"

74
00:05:57,720 --> 00:06:01,199
By standing there useless
when you were set up?

75
00:06:01,439 --> 00:06:01,939
You...

76
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:04,519
Chaosheng.

77
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:08,879
Think carefully about this.

78
00:06:09,759 --> 00:06:13,920
After all, I am currently the only one
in the family who believes

79
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:16,160
that you were set up.

80
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:20,319
I'm afraid Xuanwu
has been using you from the very start.

81
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:23,720
What you overheard

82
00:06:23,879 --> 00:06:27,120
was likely what he wanted you to hear.

83
00:06:27,759 --> 00:06:30,800
Physician Qin knows
the Mobei terrain extremely well

84
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:31,920
and escaped.

85
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:33,040
But he said

86
00:06:35,639 --> 00:06:37,720
he'd take the matter
of Master Zhaoxi to his grave,

87
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:40,360
not only to save our family's face,

88
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:42,560
but also to protect
his brother's last bloodline.

89
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:45,439
Who's there?

90
00:06:48,839 --> 00:06:50,560
It's just the wind.

91
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:01,680
Don't worry.

92
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:05,839
In business, your foresight and judgment
are unmatched by any of us.

93
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:08,920
But the Xuanji Pavilion specializes in
reading secrets and minds.

94
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:11,480
Gu Xuanwu just knew

95
00:07:12,199 --> 00:07:13,920
your weakness and used it.

96
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:28,399
Come out!

97
00:07:34,399 --> 00:07:35,160
Guards!

98
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:39,160
Catch them!

99
00:07:39,519 --> 00:07:40,240
- Yes.
- Yes.

100
00:07:53,959 --> 00:07:57,720
I brought Physician Li because I
caught a cold after hearing some songs.

101
00:07:58,279 --> 00:08:01,079
Taking him to Zhaoxi
was merely a spur-of-the-moment idea.

102
00:08:01,279 --> 00:08:03,639
I needed a reason to fish
for news about that jade pendant.

103
00:08:05,279 --> 00:08:07,120
Leng Yan was a famous assassin.

104
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:11,319
I didn't trust the Xuanji Pavilion,
so I went to him privately.

105
00:08:12,639 --> 00:08:14,839
But since Leng Yan's failure
caused no consequences...

106
00:08:15,120 --> 00:08:16,519
But Leng Yan is dead.

107
00:08:16,720 --> 00:08:17,720
That wasn't my doing.

108
00:08:19,959 --> 00:08:24,120
But I discovered Xuanji visited
his home after the incident

109
00:08:25,839 --> 00:08:27,519
and brought Wanniang
to Nichang Workshop.

110
00:08:34,560 --> 00:08:35,720
(Work Contract)

111
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:36,759
This is her work contract.

112
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:40,639
The date she arrived at the workshop
was the day after Leng Yan's murder.

113
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:43,639
She must be involved in it.

114
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:50,759
You'd already guessed
she killed Leng Yan, hadn't you?

115
00:08:50,919 --> 00:08:52,360
She ordered Wanniang to do it.

116
00:08:52,399 --> 00:08:54,240
That's why she brought her
to Nichang Workshop.

117
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:58,879
You only found these?

118
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:01,600
I intercepted the assassins
you sent to kill Wanniang.

119
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:03,080
No more tests, Chaosheng.

120
00:09:04,399 --> 00:09:07,480
I just never expected
you'd use Xuanji Pavilion agents.

121
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:10,919
Weren't you afraid the family head
would discover this?

122
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:16,039
Thank you for your candor today.

123
00:09:16,519 --> 00:09:19,919
If you remember anything else,
come to me at the Fufeng Pavilion.

124
00:09:20,799 --> 00:09:23,639
It's getting late. Sleep early.

125
00:09:23,919 --> 00:09:24,720
Wait.

126
00:09:26,559 --> 00:09:28,960
Since you've discovered Xuanji
visited Leng Yan's home,

127
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:30,759
I guess you already suspect her.

128
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:36,159
But do you know she secretly returned
a month ago to see Zhaoxi?

129
00:09:51,120 --> 00:09:53,600
Master, are you heading
to Miss Xuanji's courtyard?

130
00:10:04,240 --> 00:10:05,039
Not yet.

131
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:08,639
You've long suspected her

132
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:13,080
and found evidence
linking the missing herbs to her.

133
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:16,159
But why did you shift focus
onto Master Chaosheng instead?

134
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:20,639
Why do you think the family head
drew me into this game

135
00:10:21,559 --> 00:10:22,679
and let me marry Zhaoxi?

136
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:29,240
Using your marriage to solidify the ties
between the Pavilion and the Gus?

137
00:10:30,120 --> 00:10:30,679
Yes,

138
00:10:31,519 --> 00:10:32,440
and no.

139
00:10:33,879 --> 00:10:37,240
Whether Xuanji is really
joining hands with me

140
00:10:37,759 --> 00:10:39,120
or just shifting trouble onto me,

141
00:10:41,159 --> 00:10:44,720
even if everything traces back to her,

142
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:47,639
who do you think the family head
would deal with first?

143
00:10:48,240 --> 00:10:50,320
Her or me, the outsider in the family?

144
00:10:51,759 --> 00:10:56,799
You mean he might've long sensed
disloyalty within the family?

145
00:10:57,639 --> 00:11:00,559
I received that secret letter
implicating the Gu family.

146
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:10,000
Chaosheng heard those rumors
inciting against Zhaoxi.

147
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:11,639
And Wenshuang faced the same.

148
00:11:13,639 --> 00:11:16,039
But I couldn't understand it.

149
00:11:16,679 --> 00:11:18,440
Even with Xuanji Pavilion as leverage,

150
00:11:18,879 --> 00:11:23,279
why let me hold power
with so many Gu heirs available?

151
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:26,879
Later, I owe thanks to my husband

152
00:11:27,799 --> 00:11:29,600
for something he once said to me.

153
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:33,000
Instead of waiting
to judge others' intentions,

154
00:11:33,840 --> 00:11:35,480
why not leave them a path to goodness?

155
00:11:35,919 --> 00:11:37,639
I pondered that for a long time.

156
00:11:39,279 --> 00:11:44,559
If the family head entrusted
this matter to any one of them,

157
00:11:45,159 --> 00:11:47,240
it likely wouldn't end peacefully.

158
00:11:47,840 --> 00:11:50,720
Precisely because I'm an outsider,
I have boundaries.

159
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:54,559
After a lifetime of bloodshed,
the family head is now fading.

160
00:11:55,759 --> 00:12:00,080
He probably can't judge family affairs
by simple right or wrong.

161
00:12:01,279 --> 00:12:03,919
So my priority
isn't finding the culprit,

162
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:07,080
but securing an ally
I can fully control.

163
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:12,519
Aren't Miss Xuanji and Master Wenshuang
offering an olive branch?

164
00:12:13,360 --> 00:12:18,080
I need one I can completely control.

165
00:12:24,840 --> 00:12:25,879
What happened?

166
00:12:26,159 --> 00:12:28,759
A thief entered the master's room.
We're searching under orders.

167
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:31,600
Young Madam, see anyone suspicious?

168
00:12:32,879 --> 00:12:36,720
I just saw someone
sneaking in that direction.

169
00:12:37,159 --> 00:12:39,980
That's Miss Xuanji's courtyard. Go!

170
00:12:53,919 --> 00:12:56,960
The night is deep and cold.
Don't keep my husband waiting.

171
00:12:58,000 --> 00:12:59,000
Let's return.

172
00:13:00,399 --> 00:13:00,960
Yes.

173
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:25,279
(A Heaven task?)

174
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:28,120
(How can another Heaven task appear?)

175
00:13:29,759 --> 00:13:30,799
Yuluo's in danger.

176
00:13:53,919 --> 00:13:57,519
I thought you'd be the one
to complete this Heaven task.

177
00:13:57,799 --> 00:14:01,120
(Heaven)
But the Pavilion Master chose me.

178
00:14:03,919 --> 00:14:07,720
I wish you a successful task
and safe return.

179
00:14:09,480 --> 00:14:11,600
Do you truly wish for my safe return?

180
00:14:12,399 --> 00:14:17,024
But rumors say the family head
will reappoint a new Pavilion Master.

181
00:14:17,024 --> 00:14:17,799
You and I...

182
00:14:19,480 --> 00:14:25,000
No, all three of us could
become the next Pavilion Master.

183
00:14:25,960 --> 00:14:26,759
Xuan Qing.

184
00:14:30,960 --> 00:14:33,720
Heaven tasks serve the Son of Heaven.

185
00:14:34,799 --> 00:14:38,279
We all serve His Majesty.
No need to draw lines between us.

186
00:14:40,759 --> 00:14:43,720
It's late. Sleep early.

187
00:15:02,279 --> 00:15:05,519
Why did the family head assign
the Heaven task to Gu Xuanwu?

188
00:15:06,519 --> 00:15:09,840
- Master.
- Is the agent sent to Jiangnan back?

189
00:15:10,840 --> 00:15:11,519
Not yet.

190
00:15:12,399 --> 00:15:15,919
Then depart tomorrow and go in my stead.

191
00:15:21,320 --> 00:15:24,240
I know you find it hard to trust others.

192
00:15:24,919 --> 00:15:26,679
But you saved my life.

193
00:15:27,440 --> 00:15:29,399
I'd never betray you.

194
00:15:30,279 --> 00:15:33,440
Sending me away now means you still...

195
00:15:34,360 --> 00:15:35,480
You really are...

196
00:15:43,120 --> 00:15:44,080
"Saved you."

197
00:15:45,759 --> 00:15:49,279
But that hinges on
whether I truly saved you.

198
00:15:51,759 --> 00:15:55,080
That was your first task in Xuan Unit.

199
00:15:55,840 --> 00:15:58,816
You really think it was a coincidence

200
00:15:58,816 --> 00:16:01,120
that I was there
and brought back the dying you?

201
00:16:01,559 --> 00:16:02,159
No.

202
00:16:03,200 --> 00:16:06,279
Same as the one the family head gave you
during my Heaven task.

203
00:16:06,960 --> 00:16:08,759
During your first Earth task,

204
00:16:09,120 --> 00:16:12,399
my task was to kill you if you failed

205
00:16:12,759 --> 00:16:13,840
or were exposed.

206
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:16,120
Your task succeeded.

207
00:16:17,480 --> 00:16:19,559
That's why I brought you back.

208
00:16:20,240 --> 00:16:23,840
But when I took my Heaven task,
he assigned you the same one.

209
00:16:24,440 --> 00:16:28,200
You refused and used that opportunity
to become my death guard.

210
00:16:29,320 --> 00:16:30,320
Why?

211
00:16:32,240 --> 00:16:34,000
Master, I...

212
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:35,279
Depart tomorrow morning.

213
00:17:08,960 --> 00:17:12,800
(Vast Mind, Eternal Will)

214
00:17:28,880 --> 00:17:29,519
Thank you.

215
00:17:36,119 --> 00:17:38,200
Have you decided what to ask me?

216
00:17:46,160 --> 00:17:48,359
Seems you haven't.

217
00:17:49,440 --> 00:17:50,160
But...

218
00:17:51,400 --> 00:17:53,319
I have a question for you.

219
00:17:55,519 --> 00:17:56,480
Ask away.

220
00:17:58,279 --> 00:17:59,440
Why did you sneak into

221
00:18:01,079 --> 00:18:03,119
the head's Zhanchun Pavilion at night?

222
00:18:05,119 --> 00:18:08,200
And why did you come to this mansion?

223
00:18:09,880 --> 00:18:12,519
Wasn't it you who brought me in?

224
00:18:31,359 --> 00:18:32,720
Now, the Xuanji Pavilion...

225
00:18:49,400 --> 00:18:50,400
Where is she going?

226
00:18:52,680 --> 00:18:54,279
That is your question?

227
00:19:08,839 --> 00:19:10,079
Don't drink too fast.

228
00:19:25,839 --> 00:19:27,640
Xuan Qing is highly gifted,

229
00:19:28,400 --> 00:19:29,319
but her nature

230
00:19:30,400 --> 00:19:31,559
is too rigid.

231
00:19:32,720 --> 00:19:33,839
She doesn't belong here.

232
00:19:35,920 --> 00:19:39,079
Isn't she the only person you trust?

233
00:19:45,279 --> 00:19:46,079
Trust?

234
00:19:49,200 --> 00:19:50,400
Since I was a child,

235
00:19:51,440 --> 00:19:53,119
I've been in the Xuanji Pavilion.

236
00:19:54,319 --> 00:19:56,480
The first lesson we were taught was

237
00:19:57,039 --> 00:19:59,200
never to trust anyone.

238
00:20:37,310 --> 00:20:42,373
♪Willows sway in the twilight breeze♪

239
00:20:42,910 --> 00:20:48,231
♪Ancient alleys guard time's secrets♪

240
00:20:48,798 --> 00:20:55,426
♪Bluestones bear life's imprints♪

241
00:20:55,426 --> 00:21:00,190
♪Falling petals, endless longing♪

242
00:21:00,190 --> 00:21:02,526
♪Longing lingers within my heart♪

243
00:21:02,526 --> 00:21:09,226
♪Zither strings sigh
for the sorrow parting♪

244
00:21:09,226 --> 00:21:15,998
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

245
00:21:15,998 --> 00:21:23,134
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

246
00:21:23,134 --> 00:21:27,518
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

247
00:21:27,518 --> 00:21:30,142
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

248
00:21:30,142 --> 00:21:36,776
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

249
00:21:36,776 --> 00:21:43,326
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

250
00:21:43,326 --> 00:21:50,450
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

251
00:21:50,540 --> 00:21:54,910
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

252
00:21:54,910 --> 00:21:57,618
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

253
00:21:57,618 --> 00:22:03,518
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

254
00:22:04,158 --> 00:22:10,146
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪
